		<item>
			<title>Automann</title>
			<link>https://www.lightwavesolar.com/our-work/case-studies/automann</link>
			<guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.lightwavesolar.com/our-work/case-studies/automann</guid>
			<description><![CDATA[<p>Automann is the ultimate source for quality truck parts. As a premier global distributor of aftermarket truck and trailer chassis components, Automann serves regional warehouse distributors and repair shops with more than 30,000 products ranging from air brake &amp; wheel components to steering products – and just about everything in between.</p>
<p>In 2020 Automann completed the construction of a new 203,000 sq. ft. facility in New Lenox, Illinois. Class-A institutional-quality design &amp; construction provided Automann the ability to offer better service to their midwestern heavy duty truck parts distributors, covering 14 midwestern states.</p>
<p>As part of the state-of-the-art facility, Automann deployed a 500kW rooftop solar array. LightWave Solar teamed up with&nbsp;fellow Amicus Solar Coop member StraightUp Solar, to deliver a highly efficient and cost-effective solar project.</p>
<p><img src="https://www.lightwavesolar.com/components/com_droppics/assets/images/t.gif" alt="" style="background: url('/components/com_droppics/assets/images/gallery.png') no-repeat scroll center center #D6D6D6; border: 2px dashed #888888; height: 200px; border-radius: 10px; width: 99%;" data-droppicsgallery="17" data-droppicsversion="3.2.43" data-gallery="17" /></p>
<p>Consisting of 1,428 REC solar modules and four Solar Edge inverters, the system generates 633,055 kilowatt-hours annually which significantly reduces the facility’s energy costs. Equally important to Automann is the reduction of its electricity-related pollution. Each year, the system will reduce carbon dioxide emissions equal to taking 100 cars off the road or the carbon sequestered by 585 acres of forest.</p>
<p>Combining our companies’ strengths, LightWave proudly collaborated with fellow Amicus Solar Cooperative member StraightUp Solar to bring Automann a high performing solar system that meets their energy and sustainability goals.</p>]]></description>
